parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the autopilot and cruise control systems can cause sudden and unexpected braking, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: False Object Detection and Phantom Braking
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The false detection of objects and phantom braking can cause sudden and unexpected braking, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Autopilot Disengagement and Loss of Control
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The disengagement of the autopilot system and loss of control can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Cruise Control Malfunction and Sudden Deceleration
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the cruise control system and sudden deceleration can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
The failure of the steering system can cause the loss of control of the vehicle, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes stiff or difficult to turn
the vehicle pulls to one side
and warning messages appear on the screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Autopilot and Full Self-Driving (FSD) System Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the Autopilot and FSD systems can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly turns or changes direction without input
and warning messages appear on the screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lane Departure and Collision Warning System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lane departure and collision warning systems can cause the vehicle to drift out of its lane or fail to respond to potential collisions, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to alert the driver of lane departures or potential collisions
and warning messages appear on the screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden acceleration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries to occupants and others.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly accelerates without warning
often when the driver is not pressing the accelerator pedal
and may continue to accelerate even when the brakes are applied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected braking of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, and rear-end collisions, especially when other vehicles are following closely behind.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes without warning
often when there are no obstacles or vehicles in front of it
and may occur repeatedly during a single drive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the cruise control and autopilot systems can cause accidents, injuries, and loss of control, especially when the vehicle is traveling at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle's cruise control and autopilot systems may malfunction
causing the vehicle to suddenly brake or accelerate without warning
and may not respond to driver input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Software update issues can cause malfunctions in the vehicle's systems, leading to accidents, injuries, and loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle's software updates may not install correctly or may cause malfunctions in the vehicle's systems
